<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Architect Behind the Order | Operations Specialist</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #1B263B;
            --slate: #415A77;
            --light-slate: #778DA9;
            --sage: #84A98C;
            --off-white: #F8F9FA;
            --text-gray: #333333;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--off-white);
            color: var(--text-gray);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: var(--navy);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background: white;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .nav-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--navy);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0D1B2A 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Manifesto Section */
        .manifesto {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: white;
        }

        .manifesto-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .manifesto-text h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .accent-line {
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--sage);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Features/Differentiators */
        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: var(--off-white);
        }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--slate);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--sage);
        }

        .feature-card i {
            color: var(--sage);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Blockquote */
        .quote-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--navy);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        blockquote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* CTA Button */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--sage);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #6b8e73;
        }

        .signature {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: var(--navy);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .manifesto-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="container nav-content">
            <a href="#" class="logo">STRATEGIC OPS</a>
            <div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Complexity, Simplified.</h1>
            <p>High-level operations and systems strategy for visionary founders ready to reclaim their time and scale with intention.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Book Your Operations Audit</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="manifesto">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="manifesto-grid">
                <div class="manifesto-text">
                    <div class="accent-line"></div>
                    <h2>The Architect Behind the Order</h2>
                    <p>You didn’t start your business to spend forty hours a week inside a project management tool. You started it to innovate and lead.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p>I’m here to bridge the gap between your vision and your infrastructure. I don’t just "organize files"—I architect ecosystems that allow for sustainable growth.</p>
                    <div class="signature">Your Name</div>
                </div>
                <div style="background: var(--light-slate); height: 400px; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white;">
                    [ Professional Photography ]
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote-section">
        <div class="container">
            <blockquote>"Efficiency is not about doing more things; it’s about creating the space to do the right things."</blockquote>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">The Differentiator</h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i data-lucide="layers"></i>
                    <h3>Tactical Expertise</h3>
                    <p>Deep proficiency in the modern tech stack: Notion, ClickUp, Zapier, and Airtable.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i data-lucide="eye"></i>
                    <h3>Strategic Intuition</h3>
                    <p>I see the 10,000-foot view and the 1-inch details simultaneously to prevent bottlenecks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i data-lucide="users"></i>
                    <h3>Human-Centric</h3>
                    <p>Building systems that people actually want to use, ensuring your team adopts the change.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer style="padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; background: white;">
        <div class="container">
            <h3>Ready to build a business that runs itself?</h3>
            <br>
            <a href="mailto:hello@example.com" class="btn">Let’s Discuss Your Infrastructure</a>
            <p style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--light-slate);">© 2024 Strategic Ops Consulting. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Initialize Icons
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
